      "text": "               Constructor → build() → UI Rendered",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "A39-uW14H7zQldj2zu0nK",
      "originalText": "               Constructor → build() → UI Rendered",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zNcmJqldDgRezT0OqYEJy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 289.16017150878906,
      "y": 6913.833213329315,
      "width": 318.1243591308594,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1e",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1383398755,
      "version": 37,
      "versionNonce": 398725197,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772227776760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Explanation:\n\n1. Constructor → Widget is created\n\n2. build() method → UI is built\n\n3. If parent rebuilds → build() runs again\n\nIt does NOT have:\n\n    -> initState()\n\n    -> dispose()\n\n    -> setState()",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Explanation:\n\n1. Constructor → Widget is created\n\n2. build() method → UI is built\n\n3. If parent rebuilds → build() runs again\n\nIt does NOT have:\n\n    -> initState()\n\n    -> dispose()\n\n    -> setState()",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
